QDivorce Prediction using Ensemble ML Algorithms and Gottmans Approach to couples therapy Obtained top 6 features based on Chi-Squared value to remove any redundancy and to reduce computational cost Proposed novel ensemble models perform better than many of the standalone models in literature. Hyperparameter tuning approach and testing with various data splits resulted in accuracy of 98.24%. Research on Travelling Salesman Problem using Genetic Algorithm and Parallel Computing Enhancing the execution time of NP-hard Travelling salesman problem and comparing with related work Genetics Algorithm, Ant Colony Optimisation and Brute Force method is compared based on their time complexity and execution time. The record contains multiple attendance in order to maintain continuous presence of the students while attending classes.
